data.description: Looking for a well maintained ranch in a desirable location close to everything? Check this 2 master’s set up ranch in VB! It’s a corner lot home in a cul-de-sac.  This home boasts it’s newer wood flooring all throughout except for the bedrooms which both has newer carpet.  Granite countertop with SS kitchen appliances and new washer & dryer will convey. Roof & HVAC is only around 4 y/o. Insulated garage door was just recently replaced as well. Relax in your private covered deck at the back which has access to your other driveway great for guests & entertaining.
